high_descs: Go to the right slightly to find the stove straight back.
Pick up the pan on the left side of the stove.
Take the pan and turn around. Go to the other side of the room, and locate the fridge on the left.
Open the fridge, put the pan inside, and shut the door. Open the door, take the pan out and shut the door.
Take the pan, and turn to the left to go back to the stove.
Put the pan on the left burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Chill a pan and return it to the stove.

high_descs: Go forward and stand in front of the stove.
Pick the pan up from the left.
Go to the right and stand in front of the fridge.
Put the pan in the fridge, close the door and then open the door and take the pan back out and shut the door.
Turn and go to stand in front of the stove.
Put the pan on the bottom left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled pan on the stove.

high_descs: walk toward the white stove direct in front of you
pick up the pan small pan on the stove
turn around and carry the pan to the fridge
place the pan in the fridge to chill it. remove it when chilled
turn around and carry the pan back to the stove
put the pan back on the burner where you found it
anns.task_desc: Chill a pan in the fridge and return it to the stove
